				\begin{document}$$w\mathrm{CST} \mbox{-} \mathrm{LL}={\rm{\Sigma }}{n}_{{\rm{\max }}}[\frac{1}{10}\cdot {\rm{I}}(n)\cdot ({\rm{voxel}}\,{\rm{volume}})\cdot {\rm{weighting}}\,{\rm{factor}}]$$\end{document}wCST‐LL=Σnmax[110⋅I(n)⋅(voxelvolume)⋅weightingfactor]where nmax is the total number of intersecting voxels between the lesion volume and fiber tract and I(n) is the probability of the nth voxel (as represented in the probabilistic tract).
